title: Quixel complete pack - dDo v5.2 and nDo2 v1.16 with video tutori
description:
nDo2 v1.16 - create shader maps from normal textures with this Photoshop plugin.

dDo v5.2 - enhance your 3d model's textures with the included presets. Presets that resemble various kinds of surfaces are included. You can use the one click preview and adjust the settings later. Create great textures from base colors by just applying some presets with this Photoshop plugin.

I included one video tutorials for each program.
